<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="id121e2978-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Historical and Revision Notes</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Based on 44 U.S. Code, 1964, ed., §§ 132, 134 (<ref href="/us/act/1895-01-12/ch23">Jan. 12, 1895, ch. 23</ref>, §§ 2, 73, <ref href="/us/stat/28/601">28 Stat. 601</ref>, 612, <ref href="/us/act/1907-03-01/ch2284/s1">Mar. 1, 1907, ch. 2284, § 1</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/34/1013">34 Stat. 1013</ref>).</p>
</note>
